的育儿假，还可以给予夫妻任意一方每天一个小时的育儿时间，直至子女年满 3 周岁止。 陕西的征求意见稿中，3 周岁以内的孩子父母双方每年各有不低于 30 天的育儿假。而安徽的征求意见稿则将育儿假扩大至 6 周岁以下的孩子父母，双方每年各 10 天。14 省计生条例启动修订 首次增设不低于 10 天育儿假"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-bcba4d8535dfd763a14e3a57f8d7ade7_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/496285580"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1c6456LW/dgdEAMaCDcyNTY2ODMyIIL2h4wGMAg4oAFAKnIJNDk2Mjg1NTgweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1635933729.924521", "card_id": "Q_273750533", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 413}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有什么撩男朋友的小套路？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a6ee60c77b6d6fb63baefcc2cf99d77f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/273750533"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1c6456LW/dgdEAMaCDIzMTA4Njk4IKi129YFMAs4s2JAK3IJMjczNzUwNTMzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1635933729.9248827", "card_id": "Q_489702836", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 29}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价国产动画《识夜描银》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-76395b35436f5af978d16dae9b4e8020_1440w.gif"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/489702836"}, "text_tag_area": {"text": "导演亲自答", "font_color": "GYL01A", "background": "GYL01A"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI1c6456LW/dgdEAMaCDcxMTA0MTc5IJCsz4oGMAA4KkAscgk0ODk3MDI4MzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1635933729.9255235", "ca